# Four One AI ŌĆö Dashboard Architecture

> Generated: 2026-04-20 ┬Ę Covers Frontend, Backend & Database layers

---

## High-Level Overview

```mermaid
graph LR
    subgraph Frontend["Frontend (Angular 17+)"]
        Shell["DashboardComponent (Shell)"]
        OV["Overview Page"]
        ACT["Activity & Runs"]
        HE["Health Page"]
        PR["Purchases / Credits / etc."]
        DSvc["DashboardService"]
        LSvc["LiveDashboardService"]
    end

    subgraph Backend["Backend (NestJS)"]
        DC["DashboardController"]
        DS["DashboardService"]
        LE["LiveEventService (SSE Bus)"]
        SB["SupabaseService"]
    end

    subgraph Database["Database (Supabase / PostgreSQL)"]
        UW["user_workflows"]
        UWE["user_workflow_executions"]
        UAL["user_activity_logs"]
        KPI["get_user_dashboard_kpis()"]
        TRG["DB Triggers"]
    end

    Shell --> OV & ACT & HE & PR
    OV --> DSvc
    ACT --> DSvc
    Shell --> LSvc
    DSvc -->|HTTP| DC
    LSvc -->|SSE| DC
    DC --> DS
    DC --> LE
    DS --> SB
    SB --> UW & UWE & UAL & KPI
    TRG -.->|auto-fire| UAL
```

