## 1. Frontend Architecture

### 1.1 Component Tree

```
DashboardComponent (Shell)
Ōö£ŌöĆŌöĆ Sidebar (collapsible, 216px Ōåö 68px)
Ōö£ŌöĆŌöĆ Topbar (toggle button, page title, credits, notifications, avatar menu)
Ōö£ŌöĆŌöĆ Route Loader Overlay (classic spinner, 1.5s minimum)
Ōö£ŌöĆŌöĆ Live Execution Banner (visible on Overview & Activity only)
ŌööŌöĆŌöĆ <router-outlet>
    Ōö£ŌöĆŌöĆ OverviewComponent        /dashboard
    Ōö£ŌöĆŌöĆ ActivityComponent        /dashboard/activity
    Ōö£ŌöĆŌöĆ HealthComponent          /dashboard/health
    Ōö£ŌöĆŌöĆ PurchasesComponent       /dashboard/purchases
    Ōö£ŌöĆŌöĆ CreditsComponent         /dashboard/credits
    Ōö£ŌöĆŌöĆ InvoicesComponent        /dashboard/invoices
    Ōö£ŌöĆŌöĆ MyPaymentsComponent      /dashboard/payments
    Ōö£ŌöĆŌöĆ ProfileComponent         /dashboard/profile
    Ōö£ŌöĆŌöĆ BillingComponent         /dashboard/billing
    ŌööŌöĆŌöĆ SettingsComponent        /dashboard/settings
```

### 1.2 Key Files

| File | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `dashboard.component.ts` | Shell layout, sidebar, topbar, route loader, live banner |
| `overview/overview.component.ts` | KPI cards, charts (Chart.js), service grid, recent runs |
| `activity/activity.component.ts` | Unified feed: stats bar, status filters, paginated run list |
| `health/health.component.ts` | Per-workflow health cards with status indicators |

### 1.3 Services

#### `DashboardService` (`services/dashboard.service.ts`)

| Method | Calls | Purpose |
|--------|-------|---------|
| `loadKpis(period, from, to)` | `GET /dashboard/kpis` | All KPI data for overview |
| `loadServices()` | `GET /dashboard/services` | Purchased services grouped by category |
| `loadUnifiedFeed(page, limit, status)` | `GET /dashboard/unified-feed` | Merged activity + runs |
| `markActivityRead(ids)` | `POST /dashboard/activity/read` | Mark notifications read |
| `startAutoRefresh()` | ŌĆö | 30s polling for KPIs |
| `mapPeriodToApi()` / `getDateRange()` | ŌĆö | Period dropdown helpers |

#### `LiveDashboardService` (`services/live-dashboard.service.ts`)

| Feature | Detail |
|---------|--------|
| SSE Connection | `GET /dashboard/live?token=<jwt>` |
| State Recovery | `GET /dashboard/executions/live` on connect |
| Elapsed Ticker | Updates every 1s via `setInterval` outside Angular zone |
| Auto-Reconnect | Exponential backoff (1s ŌåÆ 30s max, 10 attempts) |
| Signals | `liveExecutions()`, `isConnected()`, `lastEvent()` |

### 1.4 State Management

All state uses **Angular Signals** (no RxJS Subjects for UI state):

```typescript
// DashboardService
kpiData = signal<DashboardKpis | null>(null);
services = signal<UserService[]>([]);
loading = signal(false);
error = signal<string | null>(null);

// DashboardComponent (Shell)
showSidebar = signal(true);
sidebarCollapsed = signal(false);
showLiveBanner = signal(false);
isRouteLoading = signal(false);
```

### 1.5 Routing

```typescript
{ path: '',         component: OverviewComponent }     // exact match
{ path: 'activity', component: ActivityComponent }
{ path: 'history',  redirectTo: 'activity' }           // legacy redirect
{ path: 'health',   component: HealthComponent }
{ path: 'purchases' | 'credits' | 'invoices' | 'payments' | 'profile' | 'billing' | 'settings' }
```

All child routes use **lazy loading** via `loadComponent`.

---

## 2. Backend Architecture

### 2.1 Module Structure

```
DashboardModule
Ōö£ŌöĆŌöĆ imports: [SupabaseModule]
Ōö£ŌöĆŌöĆ controllers: [DashboardController]
Ōö£ŌöĆŌöĆ providers: [DashboardService, LiveEventService]
ŌööŌöĆŌöĆ exports: [DashboardService, LiveEventService]
```

### 2.2 API Endpoints

| Method | Route | Auth | Purpose |
|--------|-------|------|---------|
| `GET` | `/dashboard/vitality` | No | Platform stats (influencer/affiliate pages) |
| `GET` | `/dashboard/kpis` | JWT | Per-user KPIs with period filtering |
| `GET` | `/dashboard/services` | JWT | User's purchased services + health status |
| `GET` | `/dashboard/unified-feed` | JWT | Paginated runs + stats (merged view) |
| `POST` | `/dashboard/activity/read` | JWT | Mark activity items as read |
| `SSE` | `/dashboard/live` | JWT | Real-time execution events stream |
| `GET` | `/dashboard/executions/live` | JWT | Currently running executions |
| `POST` | `/dashboard/executions/start` | JWT | Start a new execution (called by n8n) |
| `PATCH` | `/dashboard/executions/:id/complete` | JWT | Complete an execution (called by n8n) |

### 2.3 Service Methods

#### `DashboardService` (`dashboard.service.ts`)

| Method | DB Call | Returns |
|--------|---------|---------|
| `getPlatformStats()` | `purchases` table query | Revenue, purchase count, last 30 days |
| `getUserKpis()` | `rpc('get_user_dashboard_kpis')` | Full KPI JSON (single DB round-trip) |
| `getUserServices()` | `purchases` + `user_workflows` + `executions` | Services grouped by category with health |
| `getUnifiedFeed()` | `user_workflow_executions` + stats query | Paginated runs, aggregate stats, unread count |
| `markActivityRead()` | `rpc('mark_activity_read')` | `{ success: true }` |
| `startExecution()` | INSERT into `executions` + SSE emit | `{ executionId, status, startedAt }` |
| `completeExecution()` | UPDATE `executions` + SSE emit | `{ executionId, status, stoppedAt }` |
| `getLiveExecutions()` | `rpc('get_live_executions')` | Array of running executions |

#### `LiveEventService` (`live-event.service.ts`)

In-memory event bus using RxJS `Subject`:

```typescript
emit(event: LiveEvent)                          // Broadcast to all subscribers
subscribe(userId: string): Observable<MessageEvent>  // SSE stream filtered by user
```

Event types: `execution_started`, `execution_progress`, `execution_completed`, `execution_failed`

### 2.4 Live Execution Data Flow

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant n8n as n8n Webhook
    participant API as NestJS API
    participant DB as Supabase DB
    participant SSE as LiveEventService
    participant FE as Angular Dashboard

    n8n->>API: POST /executions/start
    API->>DB: INSERT execution (status: running)
    API->>SSE: emit(execution_started)
    SSE-->>FE: SSE event ŌåÆ addLiveExecution()
    Note over FE: Banner shows "1 workflow running"

    n8n->>API: PATCH /executions/:id/complete
    API->>DB: UPDATE execution (status: completed)
    Note over DB: Triggers fire: counter + activity log
    API->>SSE: emit(execution_completed)
    SSE-->>FE: SSE event ŌåÆ removeLiveExecution()
```

